{"tid":2180482,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【侵】黑人支持度升9個%","createTime":"2020-08-30T01:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T06:36:15.000Z","uid":289191,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cfcaa7415832fc6992dedcfe812a318d5f5d295e","tid":2180482,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:32:53.000Z","msg":"共和黨大會期間的民意調查，顯示在黑人當中，支持侵連任的比率，由兩周前的15%，升至24%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.breitbart.com/2020-election/2020/08/29/donald-trumps-approval-rises-nine-points-black-voters-rnc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.breitbart.com%2F2020-election%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2Fdonald-trumps-approval-rises-nine-points-black-voters-rnc%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=a36aa7f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.breitbart.com/2020-election/2020/08/29/donald-trumps-approval-rises-nine-points-black-voters-rnc/</a><br />\nPresident Donald Trump&rsquo;s approval with black voters rose nine points during the Republican National Convention, according to a Hill-HarrisX poll conducted August 22-25.<br />\nThe poll asked one question: &ldquo;Do you approve or disapprove of the job Donald Trump is doing as President of the United States?&rdquo;<br />\nThe Hill reported:<br />\nTwenty-four percent of registered black voters in the Aug. 22-25 survey, which included the first two days of the convention, said they approve of the job Trump is doing as president, while 76 percent said they disapprove.<br />\nThat is up 9 points from the previous survey conducted Aug. 8-11, where the President received 15 percent support among this group.<br />\nThe survey found support among Hispanic voters also grew by 2 percentage points, from 30 percent in the last poll to 32 percent in this most recent survey.<br />\nThe poll conducted an online survey of 2,861 registered voters. Among Republicans, 82 percent approve of Trump while 18 percent disapprove."},{"pid":"a8dae4d373a358a4dc71aa0474c98fd9d3c68e1d","tid":2180482,"uid":189404,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:35:56.000Z","msg":"BLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df029cad76106fadec2b715b5ee94b92c044ed87","tid":2180482,"uid":74361,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:37:40.000Z","msg":"唔好打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5d41c8659064d9fbbd225bec6eb841fbe20fa5","tid":2180482,"uid":12251,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:39:01.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 侵輸硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0572923dc889b1b5e704b1be9af353de48dede","tid":2180482,"uid":220942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"要等埋辯論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6f8666ffe3e3540258b5fcdd3beed92cdd13ce","tid":2180482,"uid":295224,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7c0572923dc889b1b5e704b1be9af353de48dede","tid":2180482,"uid":220942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"要等埋辯論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:54:48.000Z","msg":"辯論? 再升18%都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882ce16cc2e2bcdaa252fc80c493a0a7a22b0e28","tid":2180482,"uid":273716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7c0572923dc889b1b5e704b1be9af353de48dede","tid":2180482,"uid":220942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"要等埋辯論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:00:47.000Z","msg":"好期待睇拜登